summary: Analytical professional in domain of smart payments and compliance testing, with experience in consultancy and driving customer projects from design to success. I am always curious for a good story and finding “the why”, and that fuels my passion for making things better: improve processes, increase quality, make rational decisions, coach colleagues, and keep learning.
